# FILE: halabStore/halabStore.desc
# ROLE: High-Speed Product Catalog & Discovery Hub
# ROUTE: /store
# ACCOUNT: All account types can browse — purchase open to all
# THEME: Dark · scientific marketplace · rose/amber badge system

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- PAGE BG: bg-[#070C18] + subtle rose glow
- SIDEBAR: bg-[#0F1828] · border border-[#1E2D45] · rounded-2xl · sticky
- PRODUCT CARDS: bg-[#0F1828] · border · rounded-2xl · hover:border-[#F43F5E]/30

## 1. UNIFIED NAVIGATION SIDEBAR
- CATEGORIES: 💻 Hardware · 📐 Engineering Gear · 🏥 Medical Kits · 👕 Platform Merch
- FILTER HUD:
  - PRICE RANGE: slider (SYP) + min/max inputs
  - SOURCE TOGGLE: 🏠 منصة (platform-owned) | 🤝 وسيط (broker/vendor)
    - 🤝 wares come from Business vendor accounts
  - AVAILABILITY: ⚡ تسليم فوري | 📦 طلب مسبق

## 2. PRODUCT CARD (GRID ITEM)
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 · gap-6
- BADGE TOP-LEFT: "خصم X%" — bg-[#F43F5E] · white text
- BADGE TOP-RIGHT:
  - 🏠 منصة — teal (#14B8A6) if platform-owned
  - 🤝 وسيط — amber (#F59E0B) if from a vendor business account
- IMAGE: aspect-square · object-contain · rounded-xl · bg-[#162032]
- PRICING: original price (strikethrough gray) + student price (gradient-text bold)
- ACTIONS: [💳 حجز] quick reserve · [💬 تفاصيل] → /store/product/:id

## 3. VENDOR PRODUCTS (Business Accounts)
- Products submitted by businessType === 'vendor' appear with 🤝 وسيط badge
- Admin must approve vendor products before they appear in catalog
- Vendor name shown on product card as small attribution

## 4. EMPTY SEARCH STATE
- Card: "المنتج غير موجود؟"
- ACTION: [📲 طلب من وسيط] → WhatsApp pre-filled sourcing link

## 5. ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT
- Guest/Student/Business: can browse and purchase
- Business Vendor: sees [+ رفع منتج] button — only for their own products
- Admin: sees additional [✅ قبول] / [❌ رفض] overlay on vendor products
